    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your intoxicating petals rain down, sowing strife and destruction wherever they land. When you initiate this maneuver, all creatures other than yourself in the area must make a Will save (DC 16 + your initiation modifier) or take your weapon damage + [[/roll 8d6]] additional damage. A successful save halves this damage. Creatures that are sprouted and fail this save become staggered for a number of rounds equal to your initiation modifier.</p>"
